<seg id=1> Henan province held the trade talks with foreign financial institutions in Beijing </seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> Xinhua News Agency, Beijing, December 16th, by Haisheng Yu- Today, the government of Henan province held trade talks here with more than one hundred representatives from 88 foreign financial institutions located in Beijing. The purpose of this meeting was to enhance the mutual understanding between Henan province and the international financial institutions, and develop the means for amalgamated capital to advance the economy in Henan province. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=3> In the congratulatory message that he sent to this meeting, the vice president of the Bank of China, Yuan Chen, said that the Chinese government has decided to enlarge the developments in the middle west region of China and encourage the foreign and domestic merchants to invest in the middle west of China. The decision was also made that more than 60% of loans from foreign banks and governments will be put into the middle west region from now on. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=4> The chairman of the foreign financial institutions association in Beijing and the chief representative of Belgium Express Bank, Kexiye, indicated at the meeting that, the foreign financial institutions association in Beijing planed to contribute to the economic constructions in Henan province as well as to the developments in the middle west region of China. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=5> At the meeting, the vice permanent governor of Henan provice, Chengyu Li presented the natural resources and the economic developing situations in this province. </seg>
<seg id=6> He said that, Henan province not only has the physical conditions for foreign investments, but also has a preferential policy that is based on the national policy with the consideration of the provincial situations to encourage foreign investments and develop overseas trading and technical corporations. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=7> Concerned accountable departments of Henan province announced the business and technical corporation projects at the meeting, and discussed the related corporation intentions with the representatives attending the meeting. </seg>
</p>
